flowchart TD
    A[IOCs Schema] --> B[reports: array]
    B --> C[report item: object]

    C --> C1[url: string, uri]
    C --> C2[created: string, DD/MM/YYYY]
    C --> C3[tags: array optional]
    C --> C4[iocs: array]
    C --> C5[ttps: array]
    C --> C6[queries: array optional]
    C --> C7[infection_chain: array optional]

    R0[Required report fields: url, created, iocs, ttps] --> C

    C4 --> I1[ioc item: object]
    I1 --> I2[id: string]
    I1 --> I3[type: enum]
    I1 --> I4[value: string]
    I1 --> I5[comment: string optional]
    R1[Required IOC fields: id, type, value] --> I1
    I3 --> IT1[ip]
    I3 --> IT2[domain]
    I3 --> IT3[url]
    I3 --> IT4[sha1]
    I3 --> IT5[sha256]
    I3 --> IT6[md5]
    I3 --> IT7[process_legit]
    I3 --> IT8[domain_legit]
    I3 --> IT9[ip_legit]
    I3 --> IT10[lolbin]

    C5 --> T1[ttp item: object]
    T1 --> T2[id: string]
    T1 --> T3[comment: string]
    R2[Required TTP fields: id, comment] --> T1

    C6 --> Q1[query item: object]
    Q1 --> Q2[id: string]
    Q1 --> Q3[type: enum]
    Q1 --> Q4[value: string]
    Q1 --> Q5[iocs: array optional]
    Q1 --> Q6[comment: string optional]
    R3[Required query fields: id, type, value] --> Q1
    Q3 --> QT1[kql]
    Q3 --> QT2[yara]
    Q3 --> QT3[spl]
    Q3 --> QT4[sigma]

    C7 --> S1[step item: object]
    S1 --> S2[id: string]
    S1 --> S3[iocs: array optional refs to IOC IDs]
    S1 --> S4[ttps: array refs to TTP IDs]
    S1 --> S5[queries: array optional refs to query IDs]
    S1 --> S6[comment: string optional]
    R4[Required infection step fields: id, ttps] --> S1